tool_input.messages:
Implemented custom tooltip component for pricing section with floor pricing information. Created reusable Tooltip component with hover state management using React useState hook. Integrated with pricing display to show "Starting from $X/month" on hover with Info icon. Maintains classy, understated approach while providing pricing transparency.

```tsx
// Simple tooltip component
function Tooltip({ children, content }: { children: React.ReactNode; content: string }) {
  const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false);

  return (
    <div className="relative inline-block">
      <div
        onMouseEnter={() => setIsVisible(true)}
        onMouseLeave={() => setIsVisible(false)}
        className="cursor-help"
      >
        {children}
      </div>
      {isVisible && (
        <div className="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 mb-2 px-3 py-2 bg-gray-900 text-white text-xs rounded-lg shadow-lg whitespace-nowrap z-10">
          {content}
          <div className="absolute top-full left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-0 h-0 border-l-4 border-r-4 border-t-4 border-transparent border-t-gray-900"></div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}

// Usage in pricing component with floor pricing array
const floorPricing = [
  "Starting from $2,500/month", // Moksha Foundation
  "Starting from $8,000/month", // Ubuntu Operations  
  "Starting from $15,000/month" // Dharma Enterprise
];

<Tooltip content={floorPricing[index]}>
  <span className="text-xs text-accent font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
    {pkg.investment}
    <Info className="w-3 h-3 opacity-60" />
  </span>
</Tooltip>
```

Key implementation details: Custom tooltip with hover state, absolute positioning with arrow pointer, z-index 10 for proper layering, whitespace-nowrap for clean display, opacity-60 on Info icon for subtlety. Successfully balances pricing transparency with sophisticated presentation approach.

